item.title: Players already on?
item.dc:creator: @O_M_G1 O M G
item.description:
@O_M_G1 wrote:

I had this problem once
Many other people have…
There was one way I was able to fix it. I opened the character file, copied everything except the password and user name, had them make a new one, and pasted all the stuff into the new file. Sometimes the password gets corrupted etc…

Make sure to compile and restart in between character files
